        "conversation_id": 2,
        "reply": "To generate a memorandum for your property on BANCre, follow these steps:\n\n1. Go to the Memorandums section in your portal.\n2. Click \"Generate Memorandum.\"\n3. Select one of your existing properties from the list.\n4. The AI will process the property details, location, and any documents you've uploaded to generate a full offering memorandum.\n5. Wait for the generation to complete; you will receive a notification once it is ready.\n\nIf you encounter any issues or the memorandum is stuck on generating, remember that AI processing can take a few minutes. Refresh the page if it has been more than 10 minutes, and ensure all necessary property details and documents are uploaded correctly."
